com.iha.emulator.models.value.implemented

Class BoilerTypeActuatorValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iha.emulator.models.value.AbstractValue<java.lang.Integer>
      • com.iha.emulator.models.value.implemented.BoilerTypeActuatorValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasGenerator, HasLinearDistribution, HasNormalDistribution, Value<java.lang.Integer>, VPTRegulatorValue

    public class BoilerTypeActuatorValue
extends AbstractValue<java.lang.Integer>
implements HasNormalDistribution, HasLinearDistribution, VPTRegulatorValue
    Implementation of Value interface, extending AbstractValue representing Boiler Type actuator. Uses Integer as value data type. Provides methods for storing, generating and saving value. For generating new values uses both Normal and Linear distribution. All possible value provided by BoilerTypeActuatorValue.BoilerOperationType enum.
    Author:
    Filip Sutovsky
